trans-unit.source: The page alias is a unique reference to the page which can be called instead of its numeric ID.
trans-unit.target: Alias strani je edinstvena referenca strani, ki se lahko kliče namesto njenega številčnega ID-ja.

trans-unit.source: Trigger a 404 error if the page URL does not contain an item alias.
trans-unit.target: Sproži napako 404, kadar naslov URL ne vključuje aliasa.

trans-unit.source: A preview of the final path (possibly with placeholders) to match this page.
Optionally configure the priority to affect the order of routes. Default: 0
Please enter the page language according to the ISO-639 standard (e.g. "en" for English or "en_US" for American English).
trans-unit.target: Prosimo, vnesite jezik strani v skladu s standardom ISO-639 (npr. "en" za angleščino oz. "en_US" za ameriško angleščino).

trans-unit.source: Here you can define how search engines handle the page.
trans-unit.target: Tu lahko določite kako stran obravnavajo iskalniki.

trans-unit.source: Show visitors a page that this website is currently being maintained.
trans-unit.target: Obiskovalcem prikaži stran, da na tem spletnem mestu trenutno potekajo vzdrževalna dela.

trans-unit.source: Here you can enter a short description of the page which will be evaluated by search engines like Google or Yahoo. Search engines usually indicate between 150 and 300 characters.
trans-unit.target: Tu lahko vstavite kratek opis strani, ki ga bodo uporabili iskalniki, kot npr. Google ali Yahoo. Iskalniki navadno pokažejo med 150 in 300 znakov.

trans-unit.source: Redirect to the target page even if there are query or path parameters.
Please choose the page to which visitors will be redirected. Leave blank to redirect to the first regular subpage.
trans-unit.target: Prosimo, izberite stran kamor bodo preusmerjeni obiskovalci. Pustite prazno za preusmeritev na prvo veljavno podstran.

trans-unit.source: Redirect the member back to the last page visited instead of the redirect page.
trans-unit.target: Preusmeri uporabnika nazaj na zadnjo obiskano stran namesto na preusmeritveno stran.

trans-unit.source: Show this page if there is none that matches the visitor's language.
trans-unit.target: Prikaži to stran, če portal ne vsebuje jezika skladnega z obiskovalčevim.

trans-unit.source: Do not redirect visitors to this website root based on their preferred browser language.
trans-unit.target: Ne preusmeri obiskovalcev na to korensko stran glede na prednostno nastavljeni jezik v brskalniku.

trans-unit.source: Here you can select a favicon for the website.
trans-unit.target: Tu lahko izberete favicon za spletno mesto.

trans-unit.source: Here you can enter custom robots.txt content. It may be extended automatically by extensions.
trans-unit.target: Tu lahko vnesete vsebino datoteke robots.txt po meri. Razširitve lahko samodejno pripnejo zraven še svojo vsebino.

trans-unit.source: Here you can restrict the access to the website to a certain domain name.
trans-unit.target: Tu lahko omejite dostop do strani na določeno domeno.

trans-unit.source: The files URL applies to the files directory (page speed optimization).
trans-unit.target: URL datotek se nanaša na tl_files mapo in tudi vse male sličice (optimizacija strani za hitrost).

trans-unit.source: The assets URL applies to the assets directory (page speed optimization).
trans-unit.target: URL vtičnikov se nanaša na vse vire v plugins mapi (optimizacija strani za hitrost).

trans-unit.source: Here you can override the mailer transport used to send e-mails on this website.
Add rel="canonical" tags to the website.
trans-unit.target: Na spletno stran doda oznake rel="canonical".

trans-unit.source: Here you can set a custom canonical URL like https://example.com/.
trans-unit.target: Tu lahko nastavite "canonical URL" kot npr. https://example.com/.

trans-unit.source: By default, Contao strips the query parameters in the canonical URL. Here you can add a comma-separated list of query parameters to preserve. Use "*" as a wildcard.
E-mail address of the website administrator
trans-unit.target: Naslov elektronske pošte administratorja spletnega mesta

trans-unit.source: This e-mail address will be used to send and receive system messages.
trans-unit.target: Ta naslov elektronske pošte bo uporabljen za pošiljanje in prejemanje sistemskih sporočil.

trans-unit.source: The date format string will be parsed with the PHP date() function.
trans-unit.target: Oblika zapisa datuma bo razčlenjena s pomočjo funkcije PHP date().

trans-unit.source: The time format string will be parsed with the PHP date() function.
trans-unit.target: Oblika zapisa časa bo razčlenjena s pomočjo funkcije PHP date().

trans-unit.source: The date and time format string will be parsed with the PHP date() function.
trans-unit.target: Oblika zapisa datuma in časa bo razčlenjena s pomočjo funkcije PHP date().

trans-unit.source: Here you can select a custom character set for auto-generated aliases.
trans-unit.target: Tu lahko določite poljuben nabor znakov za samodejno ustvarjene aliase.

trans-unit.source: Generate folder-style page aliases like docs/install/download.html instead of docs-install-download.html.
Enter a URL prefix (e.g. the language) that will be prepended to all page aliases below this website root page.
The URL suffix will be added to the URI string to simulate static documents.
trans-unit.target: Končnica URL bo dodano nizu URI, s čimer bo simuliran statičen dokument.

trans-unit.source: Here you can select which protocol to use for the website.
trans-unit.target: Tu lahko nastavite protokol, ki bo uporabljen za dostop do spletnega mesta

trans-unit.source: Redirect visitors to another page (e.g. a login page).
trans-unit.target: Preusmeri obiskovalce na drugo stran (npr. vpisno stran).

trans-unit.source: Restrict page access to certain member groups.
trans-unit.target: Dostop do strani omeji le na določene skupine članov.

trans-unit.source: These groups will be able to access the page.
trans-unit.target: Skupine, ki bodo lahko dostopale do strani.

trans-unit.source: Assign a page layout to the page and its subpages.
trans-unit.target: Strani in njenim podstranem določi obliko strani.

trans-unit.source: You can manage page layouts with the "themes" module.
trans-unit.target: Postavitve strani lahko urejate z modulom "teme".

trans-unit.source: Here you can select a different layout for subpages.
trans-unit.target: Tu lahko nastavite različne postavitve za podstrani.

trans-unit.source: Set cache timeout values for the page and its subpages.
trans-unit.target: Določite življenjsko dobo strani in podstrani v predpomnilniku.

trans-unit.source: The period after which the page should no longer be considered fresh by a shared cache.
trans-unit.target: Čas po katerem stran ni več veljavna v deljenem predpomnilniku.

trans-unit.source: Always load this page from the shared cache, even if a member is logged in. Note that you can no longer personalize the page for logged in members in this case!
trans-unit.target: Stran vedno naloži iz deljenega predpomnilnika, tudi kadar je uporabnik prijavljen. Vedeti morate, da je s tem onemogočena personalizacija strani za prijavljene uporabnike.

trans-unit.source: The period after which the page should no longer be considered fresh by a private cache.
trans-unit.target: Čas po katerem stran ni več veljavna v osebnem predpomnilniku.

trans-unit.source: Access rights determine what back end users can do with the page.
trans-unit.target: Pravice dostopa določajo, kako lahko uporabniki s skrbniškimi računi urejajo stran.

trans-unit.source: Please select a user as the owner of the page.
trans-unit.target: Prosimo, izberite uporabnika kot lastnika strani.

trans-unit.source: Please select a user group as the owner of the page.
trans-unit.target: Prosimo, izberite skupino kot lastnico strani.

trans-unit.source: Please assign the access rights for the page and its subpages.
trans-unit.target: Prosimo, določite dostopne pravice strani in njenih podstrani.

trans-unit.source: Exclude the page from the search index.
The class(es) will be used in the navigation menu and the <body> tag.
trans-unit.target: CSS razredi (class) bodo uporabljeni v navigacijskem meniju in oznaki <body>.

trans-unit.source: Here you can define whether the page is shown in the HTML sitemap.
trans-unit.target: Tu lahko določite, če se stran prikaže v HTML kazalu strani

trans-unit.source: Hide the page in the navigation menu.
trans-unit.target: Ne prikaži te strani navigacijskem meniju.

trans-unit.source: A navigation item can be focused by pressing the [ALT] or [CTRL] key and the access key simultaneously.
trans-unit.target: Na element navigacije se lahko osredotočimo s pritiskom tipke [ALT] ali [CTRL] ter dostopnega ključa sočasno.

trans-unit.source: Make the page publicly visible on the website.
If you want to prevent the page from showing on the website before a certain date/time, you can enter it here. Otherwise, leave the field blank.
If you want to prevent the page from showing on the website after a certain date/time, you can enter it here. Otherwise, leave the field blank.
Enforce two-factor authentication for all members.
trans-unit.target: Zahtevaj dvostopenjsko prijavo za vse uporabnike

trans-unit.source: Please choose the page to which members will be redirected to set up two-factor authentication.
trans-unit.target: Prosimo, določite stran na katero bodo preusmerjeni vsi uporabniki, da si bodo lahko nastavili dvostopenjsko prijavo.

trans-unit.source: Show the details of page ID %s
Duplicate page ID %s with its subpages
trans-unit.target: Podvoji stran z ID %s in vse njene podstrani

trans-unit.source: Edit the articles of page ID %s
The following pages have a similar alias that may conflict with this page. If the URL is not resolved correctly, try changing the priority of the routes.
Enable canonical URLs in the website root page to enable this configuration.
